summary: Expands Tel Mithryn by adding new features, houses, enhancements, and a store SEE LONG DESCRIPTION.
descriptionHtml:
TEL MITHRYN EXPANDED AND ENHANCED-requires dragonborn
adds new features, houses, enhancements, and a store

PLAYER HOME  FOR FREE!!!                   For more player home details look at images
The player home features
-Barracks
-Bedroom/Study
-Kitchen/Dining Area
-Mage Hut
-Balcony View
-includes weapon racks, mannaquins, all crafting sets, several safe storage areas, and accurate lighting

TEL MITHRYN STORE
-The Gilded Deal
-Shopkeep who you can sell anything to except misc items
-Mainly for selling

ENHANCEMENTS
-Makes the exterior lighting accurate
-adds the Telvanni banner to most of the exterior
-adds several colorful banners inside the main tower
-ADDS TEL MITHRYNS VERY OWN GUARDS
author: DemonLord7654
